  Infrastructure

  - Docker Compose (MySQL + API + Web) + dev override
  - TypeScript strict mode — zero errors on both projects

  Next steps to run:

  cd api && cp .env.example .env  # configure secrets
  docker compose up mysql -d       # start MySQL
  npm run prisma:migrate           # run migrations
  npm run prisma:seed              # seed data
  npm run dev                      # start API on :3001

  cd ../web && npm run dev         # start frontend on :5173

